  - 'you: Wait ...  why do you have a feather in you cloak ? '
  - 'Sneak: Huh?? wait your right there is a feather in my cloak'
  - 'Sneak: i dont know how it got there mabye it just fell on me'
  - 'Sneak: There are alot of crows in this Town '
  - 'you: yea thats probably how it got there'
